re.gravatar.com/avatar/d4a21c15cca4a02a43601eed43836b1b?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/bigzepfan\">bigzepfan</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 21, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>Finally, someone who understands scheduling and not ripping you off with lame software. Great plug in, great company!\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n			<h4>Didn&#039;t get any support for something simple</h4>\n					<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">3.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-empty\"></div><div class=\"star star-empty\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/wanabrar\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4c58705f6dbb104c649c403b5524d4ec?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/wanabrar\">wanabrar</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 20, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>Was asking and waiting for 2 days to know how i could change some certain colours. Only left disappointed cuz my question gets ignored.\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n			<h4>Pleasure to work with</h4>\n					<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">5.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/rexak\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b3eb9a5a352109a2aa64b060420b4522?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/rexak\">RexAK (rexak)</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 18, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>So far, plenty of hooks and conforms to WP standards. Easy to customize and develop custom plugins for. So far.... :)\n</p>	</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-avatar\">\n		</div>\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n			<h4>The only good looking calendar with google incorporation out there</h4>\n					<div class=\"star-rating\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">5.0 rating</span><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div><div class=\"star star-full\"></div></div>		</div>\n		<p>\n			By <a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/mlgngrlbs\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/200db807f9f2f8d02fd97482cc3ec958?s=16&#38;d=monsterid&#38;r=g\" class=\"photo avatar avatar-16\" /></a>\n			<a href=\"//profiles.wordpress.org/mlgngrlbs\">mlgngrlbs</a>,\n			<span class=\"review-date\">August 18, 2016</span>\n							<span class=\"review-wp-version\">for WP 4.6</span>\n					</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">\n		<p>This plugin is awesome. The implementation is easy and the default styling itself is very nice to look at.<br />\nUsing a google calendar as source is not only easy with this plugin, it\'s also very well explained how to set it up.<br />\nWe ar